data.title: SEVP Certified Schools: April 12, 2023
data.meta_description: SEVP Certified Schools: April 12, 2023 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document is a list of schools certified by SEVP (Student and Exchange Visitor Program). It includes the school name, campus name, whether the school is fully online (F) or mixed (M), whether the campus has a physical address (C), and the city, state, and campus ID number. There are over 200 schools and campuses listed with their details.
